   Dalia Maia, Artur Campos, Univ Fed Pernambuco, Programa Posgrad Biol Anim, Recife, PE, Brazil.
   Novais Santos, Geanne Karla; do Amaral Ferraz Navarro, Daniela Maria, Univ Fed Pernambuco, Dept Quim Fundamental, Recife, PE, Brazil.
   Goncalves, Eduardo Gomes, Univ Catolica Dom Bosco, Curso Ciencias Biol, Campo Grande, Brazil.
   Alberto Nunez-Avellaneda, Luis, Univ La Salle, Dept Ciencias Basicas, Bogota, Colombia.},
